The Intuit Design for Delight (D4D) Innovator certification validates skills in human-centered design, teaching you to solve problems by deeply understanding customers, brainstorming widely, narrowing focus, and running rapid experiments. This credential proves proficiency in Intuit's innovation process, focusing on empathy, creative exploration (broad to narrow), and quick testing to build delightful customer experiences, preparing individuals to drive change in product development, CX, and strategy<br/><img src='/images/Intuit.png' width='500' height='500'>"
